*DESCRIPTION_START
A pair of women with an amazing assortment of knives strapped to their bodies
flank either side of the ladder as you climb over the rooftop edge. A number of
Fayd's less than reputable residents lounge about smoking cigarettes, playing
cards, and betting on who can land a spitball on an adventurer passing under
them on Broadway. Smaller groups of men and women stand apart from the rest of
the crowd, holding quiet discussions and passing pouches of gold back and
forth. A wide gap lays between this rooftop and the neighboring one.
