  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER The recruit is quickly blindfolded, and led towards the trapdoor that the men had been huddled around.
  ECHO OTHERS YOu are quickly blindfolded and shoved along. You hear the wooden creak of a trapdoor opening.
  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER You follow as the recruit is led down the long ladder and into an underground passage.
  ECHO OTHERS The air around you grows cool as you make the descent of the ladder blindfolded. Eventually, your feet touch down on uneven ground.
  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER You watch the recruit's face carefully as you continue along the passage and finally into the guild's rock chamber.
  ECHO OTHERS You are poked and prodded along and finally a gruff voice orders, "Stop. Wait here."
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER The recruit's blindfold is removed and the men turn around and leave.
  ECHO OTHERS The blindfold is ripped from your face and you hear the tromping of feet as the men leave you.
  AFFECT 630
  ECHO OTHERS The new recruit is led in, blindfolded, by a group of men dressed in tattered clothing.%cOne of them grins a toothless smile, tears the blindfold from the recruit's eyes, and the men turn and leave.
  AFFECT 417
  MOVEGROUP 630
 ENDIF
