NUMBER 806
NAME Musty Alley
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Stale air greets your nostrils as you move into this narrow crawlspace between
Fayd's bank and a neighboring children's toy shop. As you inch around the
enormous stone turrets of the bank, you look up to see a guard standing at 
attention at the very edge watching you carefully from the corner of his eye.
The alley opens onto Broadway to the east and Commerce to the west.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 249
EXIT W 275
ITEM 0 420 adj1=312
IFTOUCH 0
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER The guard turns to face you as you attempt to scale the stone wall of the bank.
 ECHO OTHERS The bank guard on the rooftop turns to face %n.
 PLREVENT 1
 CONTPLREVENT
 IFVAR ORG = 3
  ECHO PLAYER With a quick flash of your badge, you receive a formal salute from him as he states, "All's well officer. No need to come up here."
  ECHO OTHERS He salutes %n and states, "All's well officer. No need to come up here."
 ENDIF
 IFVAR ORG = 6
  ECHO PLAYER He seems to recognize you as a member of the Crimson Band, nods respectfully and states, "All's well up here, sir."
  ECHO OTHERS He appears to recognize %n, nods respectfully and states, "All's well up here."
 ENDIF
 IFVAR ORG ! 3
  IFVAR ORG ! 6
   ECHO PLAYER He levels his pike at your forehead and bellows, "Off with you!"
   ECHO OTHERS He levels his pike at %n's forehead and bellows, "Off with you!"
  ENDIF
 ENDIF
ENDIF
