NUMBER 807
NAME Windy Alley
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The narrow width of this alley causes even the slightest breeze to whistle
through with an almost melodic humming tone. The sound of children playing
within their home floats merrily out of a second floor window. To the south,
the alley becomes impassable as the homes grow even closer together.
*DESCRIPTION_END
