NUMBER 808
NAME Dark Crawlspace
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Crawling on your hands and knees, you squeeze yourself into the unbearably
tight space created by two homes leaning into each other. Your feet sink
slightly into the muddy earth as you stop to fight back a wave of 
claustrophobia. The crawlway continues to the south, from which a fresh breeze
brushes your face. To the north is the alley off of Tilvaen Road.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 809
EXIT N 807
