NUMBER 837
; NAME Tilvaen Manhole
NAME Manhole
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
This has got to be the cleanest underground passage you've seen in all of
Fayd.  There's a slight musty smell, but no foulness to speak of.  A few
lost aelven toys have fallen through the gutters and float in the
few inches of drainage before the passage west.  A sturdy ladder has been
carefully attached to one wall, leading out of this abysmally cheery sewer.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_GROUND
FIXED_LIGHT
EXIT W 893
; a ladder (leading to Tilvaen (#6934))
ITEM 0 449 val2=6934
IFPREVERB CLIMB 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The manhole is sealed shut.
ENDIF
