NUMBER 838
NAME Stinking Nexus
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
It would be a testament to willpower to stay in this part of the sewers for
long.  All of the various parts of the water drainage network funnel their
cloudy, murky and smelly wet offal to this location from every end of Fayd.
To the west, the flow of black-gray water heads out of town.  Just as
quickly, more retch pours in from the south, east, and even overhead.  The
uneven splashing sound alone is enough to make you feel ill.  The unearthly
light from a sputtering torch someone's placed here doesn't help.  The pipe
from above has some metal rungs affixed.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_GROUND
FIXED_LIGHT
; MONSTER_GROUP 211
EXIT W 848
EXIT E 847
EXIT S 897
EXIT U 839
; some black-grey water
ITEM 8 198 adj1=1094
;
;
NUMBER 839
NAME Sludge Ridge
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The disgusting smell and the rushing water are crashing in from both sides.
From the southeast and the northwest, two sloping tunnels spews forth a 
black-gray water flow which has an undescribable texture.  The water is forced
across a large flat depression in this stone chamber, in the vain hopes that 
some of the heavier waste is trapped before falling through the chute in the
floor.  You can make out some iron handholds bolted in the downward passage.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_GROUND
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
; MONSTER_GROUP 211
EXIT NW 900
EXIT SE 899
EXIT D 838
; going down always works, but you might be clumsy
IFPREVERB D -1
  CLEARVERB
  DISBAND
  SKILLCHECK 10 0 DUMMY1
  IFVAR DUMMY1 >= 0
    ECHO PLAYER You swing down to the chamber below on the provided handholds.
    ECHO OTHERS %N grabs the handhold and swings down to the chamber below.
    MOVE 838
    AFFECT 838
    ECHO OTHERS %N swoops in from above and lands deftly on %h feet!
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You reach for a handhold, but miss!  A wave washes you over the dam.
    ECHO OTHERS %N reaches for a handhold, and next thing you know, %s's gone!
    POSITION LAY
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
    MOVE 838
    AFFECT 838
    APPEAR %S is sopping wet to the waist with a black-gray liquid, and Oh! the stench!
    ECHO OTHERS %N is washed into the room on %h backside!
  ENDIF
ENDIF
