NUMBER 845
NAME Black Bog
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Fresh air and water from the Eltinmar valley mingle with the worst slime and
stench you could imagine.  A battle between nature and civilization is
taking place here, a wide bowl-shaped depression in the muddy river bank.
Some hardy gray reeds poke through the sludge, and you can see several types
of insects flapping their way across the slick surface.  A soggy black
passage winds over a ridge to the south.  Without looking, you can make out
a foul-smelling opening into a pipe leading back towards the town of Fayd.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_GROUND
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
