*DESCRIPTION_START
This part of the sewer system seems to be the highest point, and thus, the
dryest.  In both directions, north and south, the floor slopes very slowly
downward.  You can easily make out the sounds of commerce, through the
oversized storm grates that hardly cause a trickle of water.
*DESCRIPTION_END
