*DESCRIPTION_START
Gray and black water sloshes violently up the wall here, and settles into a
rushing river headed north.  You can make out the curve in the sewer to the
south, as well as many inlets and holes pouring more water from the busy
businesses and homes on Pleasant Avenue.
*DESCRIPTION_END
