NAME Sewers under Broadway
; from pq894 to broadway892
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The tunnel under Broadway is just as dark as the street itself is.  There is
very little light filtering through the sparse storm drains.  You can't avoid
the constant gurgling noise of the ugly river of unimaginable filth.  A thin
but serviceable walkway keeps your feet somewhat dry.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_GROUND
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
