NUMBER 899
NAME Sewers under City Hall
; from lance896 to ridge839
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Somewhere near here, the tunnel bends to connect Elm's drainage ways with
those of another street.  To the south, the floor rises gradually to a
high point, and to the northwest, it starts to descend more rapidly with
a stronger flow of water.  You can tell you're under the City Hall here
because the ceiling has been meticulously finished, patched and repaired
to thwart any spying or jail escapes. There isn't one solitary remaining
gap, crack, crevice or opening in the stone overhead.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_GROUND
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
EXIT S 896
EXIT NW 839
; a tiny hole (peeks into City Hall's Lockup (#340))
ITEM 0 79 adj1=327 val2=899
IFPREVERB LOOK 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You peer through a tiny hole...
  ECHO OTHERS %N looks up.
  SHOWROOM 340
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You'd never fit.
ENDIF
