; a chute descending into darkness
ITEM 5 1508 val2=894
 EXTEND 5 descending into darkness
IFPREVERB GO 5
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You might be able to slide down.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB D -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR SITTING = 1
    DISBAND
    ECHO PLAYER You slip down the chute feet-first!
    ECHO OTHERS %N wriggles %h feet down into the chute, and slides out of sight!
    MOVE 894
    AFFECT 894
    ECHO PLAYER The chute ends before it reaches the floor.
    ECHO OTHERS %N slides in from above, and drops to the floor with a bump!
    POSITION LAY
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 5
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You might be able to slide down the chute, but only feet-first.
  ENDIF
ENDIF

